  "translations": {
    "en": "Ali ibn Isa (may God be pleased with him) narrated to us. He said: Ali ibn Muhammad Majiluwayh narrated to us. He said: Ahmad ibn Abi Abdillah narrated to us, from his father, from al-Husayn ibn Ilwan al-Kalbi, from Amr ibn Thabit, from Zayd ibn Ali, from his father, from his grandfather (peace be upon them). He said: Amir al-Mu'minin Ali ibn Abi Talib (peace be upon him) said: Indeed, in",
    "ur": "ہم سے علی بن عیسیٰ (رضی اللہ عنہ) نے بیان کیا ... امیر المؤمنین علی بن ابی طالب (علیہ السلام) نے فرمایا: بے شک",
    "tr": "Ali bin İsa (radıyallahu anh) bize anlattı ... Müminlerin Emîri Ali bin Ebî Tâlib (aleyhisselam) buyurdu: Şüphesiz",
    "fa": "علیّ بن عیسی ... امیرالمؤمنین علیّ بن ابی‌طالب (علیه السلام) فرمود: همانا در",
    "id": "Ali bin Isa menceritakan kepada kami ... Amirul Mukminin Ali bin Abi Thalib bersabda: Sesungguhnya di",
    "bn": "আলী ইবনে ঈসা ... আমীরুল মুমিনীন আলী ইবনে আবি তালিব বলেছেন: নিশ্চয়ই",
    "es": "Ali ibn Isa nos narró ... Ali ibn Abi Talib dijo: Ciertamente, en",
    "fr": "Ali ibn Isa nous a raconté ... Ali ibn Abi Tâlib a dit : Certes, dans",
    "de": "Ali ibn Isa erzählte uns ... Ali ibn Abi Talib sagte: Wahrlich, im",
    "ru": "Али ибн Иса рассказал нам ... Али ибн Аби Талиб сказал: Воистину, в",
    "zh": "阿里·伊本·伊萨给我们讲述了 ... 阿里·伊本·阿比·塔利布说：确实，在"
  }
}